Package: vzlogger
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: program for logging measurements to a volkszaehler.org middleware
 vzlogger...
  * is a tool to read and log measurements from a wide variety of smartmeters and
    sensors to the volkszaehler.org middleware.
  * can run as a daemon or via cron.
  * includes a tiny onboard httpd to serve
    realtime readings to the AJAX web frontend.
  * is written in ISO C++ and should run on most embedded devices
    which conform to the POSIX standard.

Package: vzlogger-dbg
Architecture: any
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Depends: vzlogger (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Debugging symbols for vzlogger
 This package contains the debugging symbols for vzlogger.

